Text: After last week's episode coming in a day early & being legit I won't question this one... I'll just say thanks for making this available before I can see it on tv later tonight!! :)
Loved this episode... but not liking the way they're taking the show!! Hope they don't do what it looks like they are implying in this episode!!
Day early because In Canada it is shown on Mondays. In USA on Tues.
